content:
Track MCG assessments with the Assessment History component. This gives care managers an overview of every instance, including status and submitted date. Care managers can monitor patient progress without navigating to other pages.

Where: Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Health Cloud.
Who: Users with Care Plans Access permission set license and MCG API credentials.
How: Turn on MCG Care Guidelines in Setup, place DiscoveryFrameworkAssessmentHistory FlexCard on assessment record page, and add MCG integration definition.
title: Track MCG Assessment History in Salesforce Health Cloud
